Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:51.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kurono? Nie, nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kurono! Kurono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, nie, nie nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.69,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kurono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:37.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pozrite na moje žiarivé vlasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Starajte sa o svoje vlasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.32,wARNS,,0,0,0,,Mimoriadne správy:\NOsaka je v núdzovom stave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo sa v Osake deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:49.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Žeby monštrá, ako v Shibuyi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,-OSAKA JE V NÚDZOVOM STAVE.\N-SI V PORIADKU?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,-AKO TIE VRAŽDY V TOKYIU.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:02.49,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Obsahuje obohatenú \Nkyselinu hyalurónovú, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,JE TO ARMÁDA SPOJENÝCH ŠTÁTOV?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Som v Shinjuku, Ayumu. Chytím si vlak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Meškáš. Čo si robil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pamätáš si, aký je dnes deň?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo je za deň?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Má nôž!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Polícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde ste zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budete v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:41.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Všetko najlepšie Ayumu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja... žijem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej, ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si v šoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dobodali... ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.39,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dobodali?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:37.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja som dostal porážku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:41.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tuto Reika mala autonehodu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tá hviezda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ó áno, je veľmi známa, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:55.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Som trochu mimo diania...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale videl som ju v TV reklame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,No na čo? Tuším šampón...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prosím. Koho to zaujíma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.88,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie si jej fanúšikom, Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poznám študentov....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čuš dedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ako sa voláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato Masaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja som Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.39,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Teší ma, Kato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.49,MCSG,,0,0,0,,O čo tu ide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hovor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ťažko tomu veriť,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,ale umreli sme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kvákal si mi to isté.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nedáva to zmysel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:56.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Povstaňme, je tu nové ráno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:09:00.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ráno nádeje{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.50,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dýchajme s hruďou plnou radosti{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:08.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pozrime na jasnú, modrú oblohu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Počúvajme rádio{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Letný vánok je tak zdravý{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:20.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nadýchnime sa a rozcvičme{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:25.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Na raz, dva, tri{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vaše staré životy skončili.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:40.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rozhodnem ako vás použiť. \NTak to chodí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:46.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choďte a porazte túto bytosť:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nurarihyon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,ZABITE HO V URČENOM ČASE.\NJE DOBRÝ. NEVZDÁ SA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.82,MCSG,,0,0,0,,No nie. Vyzerá nebezpečne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo je to za vec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.82,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tá čierna guľa je... Gantz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:06.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Neviem prečo, ale tak to všetci volajú.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo je to do pekla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To sú detské hračky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,,,Kato-cha, LOL." To je moje?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:31.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Radšej sa oblečte, začiatočníci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:36.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nehovor mi čo mám robiť, dedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.70,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kreténi ako on vždy zomrú prví.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo si to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty si len sprostý hráč.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Máš ty ale spôsoby, študentík.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hovorím s tebou, blbec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nishi!\NPrestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.88,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vravel som.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Iba by nás brzdil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tento tiež vyzerá na nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Daj si ten oblek, Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sme uväznený v nekonečnej hre o prežitie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hra o prežitie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:54.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musel si to vidieť v správach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:57.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počul si o príšerách v Shibuyi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,S takými bojujeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:05.70,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takže, vy ste tí v čiernych oblekoch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:13.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,V minulej hre sme nanešťaste \Nprišli o najsilnejších členov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Stratili sme nášho vodcu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz, zober ma odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Rýchlo Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ponáhľaj sa, prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Obleč si ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ste v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.25,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkať...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,DOTONBORI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,My sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.09,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:56.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale vždy nás posielal do Tokia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.87,Zbr,,0,0,0,,MIMO DOSTREL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je mimo dostrel, ty kretén.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.14,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku, Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vy ste na nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.46,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, spanikáril som.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.50,MCSG,,0,0,0,,O čo tu ide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vysvetlite mi to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pojeb sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.82,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?! Čo je zač?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prečo mi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkaj Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:27.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetko mu vysvetlím!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.44,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prečo s nimi musíme bojovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,A čo sú zač?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nevieme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.86,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vieme len jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:50.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musíme všetky zabiť, než nám vyprší čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo ak by sme to nestihli?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetci by sme zomreli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:05.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Naozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Viac by sme neexistovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To sú pravidlá Gantz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo myslíš tým ,,pravidlá"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.47,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poď sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tadiaľto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.10,Zbr,,0,0,0,,PREBÍJANIE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato strieľaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.24,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oblek ťa ochránil. Poď!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kto to spravil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,--Vskutku?\N--Klame!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo sú zač?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:24.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Máte Tokijský prízvuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vy ste tím Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tím Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.46,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takže nás je viac?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Akože to nevieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Toto je jeho prvá hra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:44.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nováčik, decko, muž \Nv strednom veku a žena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tomu vravím zúfalstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.40,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:20:01.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pokiaľ prežiješ, \Nkončatiny sa ti na konci hry obnovia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.40,MCSG,,0,0,0,,keď sú zabité všetky monštrá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.16,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čože...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:10.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde je ten frajer Kuro \Nalebo ako sa to volá?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkať!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To je Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Wau, pozri na tie prsia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hergot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tím Tokyo na tom nakoniec nie je tak zle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ďalší!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je to tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Len seďte a dívajte sa, nuly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:56.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Reika, pozeraj ako s nimi zatočíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Potom si môžme vymeniť čísla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej, George! Poď!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je ich tu toľko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pôjdem zprava.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.40,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:19.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Užívajú si to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:33.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tá je za veľa. Postarám sa o to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo ty na to Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:13.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Osaka tím je silný.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:17.44,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Odkiaľ majú tú zbraň a motorku?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:25.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak získaš sto bodov, \Nmôžeš si vybrať lepšie zbrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:26.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sto bodov?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:33.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Potom čo vyhráme nás hra pošle späť \Ndo miestnosti, kde sme obodovaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,100 BODOVÉ MENU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:39.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak získaš stovku, vyhral si.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:47.02,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz ti potom dá vybrať z troch bonusov.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:48.69,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bonusov?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:52.16,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžeš mať lepšie zbrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Alebo vzkriesiť mŕtveho spoluhráča.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:57.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžeš ho oživiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.51,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zjavne. Nikdy som to nerobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,A tretia možnosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:05.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,3. VYMAZANIE SPOMIENOK A KONIEC.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Výhra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:08.48,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budeš voľný!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.19,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ako to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Získaj sto bodov a môžeš \Nnechať toto všetko za sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:19.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zabudneš všetko o Gantz a vrátiš \Nsa do normálneho života.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.17,0:24:24.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak sa to tak vezme, takto \Nje to lepšie. Nie Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:27.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemusíme robiť nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.98,0:24:31.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tím Osaka pobije všetky príšery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.12,0:24:37.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Malé im nechám a zabijem bossa na konci.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:45.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nishi sa chce skryť a počkať na \Nnajsilnejšiu príšeru na konci.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.09,0:24:49.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Za zabitie bossa je veľa bodov.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:51.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pomôžte!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:02.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musíme im pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:04.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poď Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.59,0:25:08.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mali by sme sa vyhnúť zbytočným rizikám.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.79,0:25:09.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.06,0:25:13.77,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale nemáte snáď zachraňovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:15.70,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie bez nášho vodcu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.90,0:25:17.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poď!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.14,0:25:23.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie sme dosť silní na to,\N aby sme chránili iných.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:41.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nechajme to na tím Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.39,0:25:47.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sústreďme sa len na prežitie. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:51.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato počkaj! Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:58.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak musíš ísť, zober si to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.95,0:26:04.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Niekto čaká až mu zavoláš.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.89,0:26:08.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,V okolí by mali byť nejaké telefónne búdky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.78,0:26:17.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Uisti sa, že nezomrieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.70,0:26:50.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:54.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetká omáčka len pre nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:05.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vidíš to?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.51,0:27:10.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.88,0:27:14.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To nie je socha Biriken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.53,0:27:23.82,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá strašideľne.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.28,0:27:39.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Katov byt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.17,0:27:42.77,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.38,0:27:46.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ayumu, to som ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.86,0:27:51.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde si? Volal som ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.13,0:27:53.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.19,0:27:56.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musel som ísť do práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.91,0:27:59.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takto v noci?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:03.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,A ešte keď sa v Osake dejú také veci?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.74,0:28:07.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo sa tam deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:11.69,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Besnia tam príšery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.13,0:28:14.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.41,0:28:17.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To som nevedel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.02,0:28:21.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ako je to vôbec možné? \NTo je jedno. Príď už!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.44,0:28:24.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.67,0:28:27.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chvíľu to potrvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:32.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ok. Tak neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:33.39,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ayumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.29,0:28:35.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.08,0:28:41.02,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vrátim sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.16,0:28:46.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Viem!\NNajem sa a pôjdem spať.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.31,0:29:05.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.20,0:29:20.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dokelu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.38,0:30:33.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zdravím!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.80,0:30:39.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty si s tímom Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:42.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.68,0:30:47.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Som z Osaka tímu. Anzu Yamasaki. A ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.16,0:30:51.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Masaru Kato.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.71,0:30:55.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Koľko máš rokov? Ja 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.00,0:30:57.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sedemnásť.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.61,0:30:59.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Stredoškolák!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:01.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si ešte len dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.65,0:31:07.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sledovala som ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.87,0:31:14.47,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zaujalo ma... čo si robil.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.70,0:31:18.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Iste sa mýlim, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.19,0:31:22.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zachránil si tú rodinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.43,0:31:27.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,O čo ti skutočne šlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.59,0:31:28.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.73,0:31:31.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chcel som ich zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.84,0:31:35.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bože, to je nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.11,0:31:36.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Spravil som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.14,0:31:38.25,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie! Nikto to nerobí.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.52,0:31:40.24,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale ja áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.47,0:31:44.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty by si sa kľudne dívala, \Nako niekoho zabijú?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.93,0:31:48.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prestrojený mimozemšťan!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:55.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si naštvaný?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.13,0:31:57.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budem pomáhať ľudom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.36,0:32:00.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prestaň s tým.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.52,0:32:02.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pokrytec.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.43,0:32:05.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nechoď za mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.69,0:32:10.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zvoľni! Rada sledujem čudákov.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.87,0:32:14.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si zábavný!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.92,0:32:19.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Viem, že dlho nevydržíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.84,0:32:24.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Práve som si spomenula.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:29.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Videla som starých ľudí \Nskrývať sa i s dieťaťom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.51,0:32:31.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že sú v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.57,0:32:33.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde sú?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:37.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty sa ale predvádzaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.51,0:32:45.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Neplač, lebo nás tie príšery nájdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:48.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je po nás. Je to tu ako v pekle!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.78,0:32:54.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja môžem zomrieť, ale chlapec nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:57.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Má pred sebou celý život.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.45,0:33:00.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chcem ho zaniesť rodičom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.42,0:33:05.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Choď  od toho!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.18,0:33:09.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bežte! Postáram sa o to!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.24,0:33:10.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Drahý!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.06,0:33:22.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Drahý!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:28.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Drahý!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:37.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tam sú.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.41,0:33:40.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ste v poriadku?! Zachránim vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.46,0:33:43.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ustúpte!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.55,0:33:47.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Uteč!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:50.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie. Zachránim ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.13,0:33:53.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemožné! Nemôžeš ho poraziť!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.97,0:33:58.44,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zachránim ich.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.62,0:34:00.63,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Neopovažuj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.73,0:34:03.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Viem, že sa bojíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:07.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zomrieš, ty hlupák!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:14.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prestaň! Vážne ťa zabije!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.43,0:34:15.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.69,0:34:22.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak si chce umrieť, môže.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.41,0:34:25.65,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je to len kretén...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.99,0:34:31.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hoci... je celkom roztomilý.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.81,0:34:35.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžem nejako pomôcť, chlapče?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.77,0:34:37.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Choďte preč.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.96,0:34:40.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hlupáci ako on sú vzácni.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.20,0:34:43.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Jeden taký...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.69,0:34:53.39,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ustúpte!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.19,0:34:56.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.85,0:35:02.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Možno sa bojím,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:06.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,že zomrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.29,0:35:30.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ako ho môžem poraziť?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.74,0:35:35.65,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To je idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.41,0:35:47.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Do riti!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:21.69,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:02.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:32.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.16,0:37:38.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:43.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej, si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.65,0:38:05.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je tu doktor alebo zdravotník?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.12,0:38:10.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zavolajte niekto sanitku!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.04,0:38:16.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hlavné ťahy sa hemžia ľudmi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.79,0:38:23.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Experti tvrdia, že tie stvorenia \Nsú mimozemského pôvodu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.39,0:38:26.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chystáš sa zachraňovať ďalších?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.27,0:38:31.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.89,0:38:37.50,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prečo sa chováš ako nejaký hrdina?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.99,0:38:40.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nerieš to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.86,0:38:46.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Len ma zaujíma tvoja výchova.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.44,0:38:51.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo robia tvoji rodičia?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.06,0:38:54.40,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Moji rodičia?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.88,0:38:58.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Otec bol hasič.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:39:01.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zomrel aj s mamou pri autonehode.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.94,0:39:04.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bol som v prváku na strednej.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.24,0:39:09.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Máš súrodencov?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.32,0:39:12.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Desaťročného brata.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:15.06,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je v sirotinci?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.80,0:39:19.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pracujem, môžeme si dovoliť byt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.83,0:39:25.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak neprežiješ, tvoj brat ostane sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.64,0:39:27.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.44,0:39:31.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ja žijem so svojim trojročným synom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.54,0:39:34.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty si mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.35,0:39:37.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej. Vyzerám snáď primlado?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:45.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kedykoľvek sa ťa takto \Nspýtajú povedz len ,,áno"!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:55.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Inak, obaja sme v rovnakej situácií.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.30,0:39:58.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme si dovoliť umrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.01,0:40:00.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nikdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.71,0:40:03.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.11,0:40:07.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme zomrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.58,0:40:17.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Armádne jednotky boli \Nnasadené po celom meste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:23.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Máme nové informácie o záhadných \Nľudoch v čiernych oblekoch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:28.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tento záznam sa pred \Nchvíľou objavil na internete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.36,0:40:34.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je na ňom mladý muž v čiernom, \Nktorý ochraňuje starší pár s dieťaťom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.54,0:40:41.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,EXISTUJÚ!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.51,0:40:42.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,PÔSOBIVÉ.\NDO TOHO OSAKA!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.70,0:40:46.10,MCSG,,0,0,0,,-VIDEL SI SPRÁVY?\N-JE TO SKUTOČNÉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.14,0:40:48.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,-PODĽA TV HEJ...\N-DO TOHO ČIERNOODENCI!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.45,0:40:57.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Choďte!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.73,0:40:58.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vďaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.49,0:41:11.88,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Použi tú veľkú!\NEšte nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.93,0:41:13.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Spravím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.44,0:41:17.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je na nich niečo šialené...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.17,0:41:24.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takí ako oni vždy prežijú.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.00,0:41:27.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ten tmavý,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.96,0:41:30.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,voláme ho George.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.68,0:41:33.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Jeho pravé meno je Shimaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.81,0:41:35.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyhral už tri bonusy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.22,0:41:39.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dlhý skinhead je Nobuo Muroya.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.30,0:41:42.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Voláme ho Nobuyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.06,0:41:45.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyhral už štyrikrát.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.51,0:41:52.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je bezohľadný megalomaniak \Na egocentrický vodca.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.15,0:41:54.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.12,0:41:57.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je tu ešte niekto.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.05,0:41:59.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Skutočne?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:04.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hachiro Oka, sedemnásobný víťaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.72,0:42:07.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Niekde je.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.48,0:42:11.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Skrýva sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.88,0:42:25.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.84,0:42:41.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že Kato je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.11,0:42:46.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo ti je?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.79,0:42:50.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak by Kurono žil,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.19,0:42:54.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,zachraňoval by takých ako Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.80,0:42:59.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Som si istý, že áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.77,0:43:05.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžeme Kurona oživiť, ak získame sto bodov
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.79,0:43:09.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemáme šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.93,0:43:11.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale Suzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.34,0:43:15.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sotva sa postaráme o seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.86,0:43:21.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.06,0:44:17.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Jeden je tu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.66,0:44:24.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je s nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.63,0:44:52.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Boss by mal byť za stovku.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.27,0:44:56.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sto bodov za jednu príšeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.48,0:44:58.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Áno, sto za jednu.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.94,0:45:04.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tie príšery na veži vyzerajú silne.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.34,0:45:07.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Za jednu nezískaš stovku.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.80,0:45:11.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oka vraví, že sa to stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.42,0:45:12.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.28,0:45:17.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bolo to predtým, než sme \Nprišli do miestnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.41,0:45:21.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetci okrem Oka zomreli.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.45,0:45:23.88,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oka zabil bossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.13,0:45:25.82,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sám!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.56,0:45:29.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,On je príšera!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.65,0:45:47.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.36,0:45:50.09,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.77,0:45:53.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je mimo našu ligu.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.93,0:45:56.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ani hnúť! Ruky nad hlavu!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.43,0:45:59.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.25,0:46:02.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nestrieľajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.54,0:46:06.92,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.17,0:46:08.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prestaňte strieľať!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.70,0:46:12.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vy v čiernom! Čo ste zač?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.39,0:46:14.22,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budem strieľať!\NPočkať!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.71,0:46:19.16,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sme agenti.\NAká jednotka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.20,0:46:20.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Naša jednotka je...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.89,0:46:22.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.35,0:46:25.06,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.02,0:46:30.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Má ešte väčšie problémy!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.57,0:46:32.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ukážte identifikácie!\NŽiadne nemáme.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.11,0:46:34.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale je to pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.29,0:46:36.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budem strieľať!\NNie!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.34,0:46:37.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.56,0:47:00.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Páľte!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.01,0:47:06.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetci utekajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.76,0:47:24.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Postaraj sa oňho!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.90,0:47:49.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poď si po mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.83,0:47:50.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.27,0:48:32.77,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.13,0:48:54.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takže?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.89,0:48:57.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.67,0:49:01.22,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To si robíš prdel.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.25,0:49:09.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.90,0:49:11.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je za sto?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.26,0:49:13.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vybavím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.86,0:49:21.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Keď skončím, budeš tenší ako papier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.79,0:49:37.86,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si silák, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.93,0:49:39.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Šváb jeden.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.99,0:50:05.67,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nefilmuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.40,0:50:10.24,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zmrd!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.14,0:50:23.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kurva, kurva, kurvááá!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.53,0:50:27.30,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Pomôž mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.35,0:50:33.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo je? Nevieš sa postarať o svoj zadok?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.64,0:50:54.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Stavím sa, že si si narobil \Ndo gatí. Čo Muroya?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.82,0:51:05.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kurva...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.97,0:51:09.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nobuyan...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.49,0:51:11.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.84,0:51:28.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takže ty si boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:31.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ten starček?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.87,0:51:41.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mám ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.93,0:52:01.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.91,0:52:05.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:08.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.84,0:52:55.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dostal som ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.25,0:53:20.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To nemôže byť pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.23,0:53:22.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Obaja sú mŕtvy!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.33,0:53:28.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo chceš spraviť?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.61,0:53:31.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Len to...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.13,0:53:33.64,MCSG,,0,0,0,,čo môžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.87,0:53:35.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zomrieš!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.73,0:53:37.86,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mysli na svojho brata!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.91,0:53:40.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Preto to musím spraviť.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.91,0:53:43.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Inak...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.32,0:53:46.03,MCSG,,0,0,0,,všetci zomrú.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.46,0:53:50.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale ako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.87,0:53:55.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej! Hej!\NNebuď hlúpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.91,0:54:32.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,U-Uhýba sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.50,0:54:45.16,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je moc rýchla.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.53,0:54:47.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Spoločne!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.48,0:55:13.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Trafil som ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.23,0:55:28.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zásah do hlavy neúčinkuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.71,0:55:34.02,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kri ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.46,0:55:42.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Aymu, sľubujem,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.88,0:55:45.88,MCSG,,0,0,0,,že prídem domov!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.37,0:56:39.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dostal som bossa!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.35,0:56:55.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Takmer si nás odpálil!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.80,0:56:57.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tragédia!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.94,0:57:00.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mieril som na rameno.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.01,0:57:07.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zvládli sme to...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.53,0:57:10.49,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Porazili sme tím Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.79,0:57:31.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.87,0:57:34.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to znamená?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.14,0:57:40.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ajaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.55,0:58:02.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bežte.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.95,0:58:09.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Utečte!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.73,1:00:07.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prehrali sme...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.48,1:00:09.08,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie. Pozri.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.89,1:00:21.23,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To je Oka!\NOka?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:23.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hachiro Oka!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.46,1:00:39.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dostal ju!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.42,1:00:55.23,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Stále krváca.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.86,1:00:59.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej, počuješ ma?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.16,1:01:03.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato... pozri sa!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.96,1:01:08.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Žije.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.96,1:01:09.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dokelu!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.42,1:01:15.77,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.95,1:01:22.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak žiješ do konca hry, uzdravíš sa?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.30,1:01:24.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ááá... uhm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.55,1:01:30.51,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Keď ho Oka rýchlo porazí, pomôže mu to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.16,1:01:45.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je príliš silný!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.84,1:01:48.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ani neviem, ako na mňa zaútočil.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.27,1:01:52.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oka to zvládne
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.97,1:01:54.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Porazí ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.55,1:01:59.36,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hachiro Oka vyhral už sedemkrát.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.20,1:02:23.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mýliš sa, keď si myslíš, \Nže ma porazíš, zelenáč!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.72,1:02:36.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Na univerzite som hrával ping pong!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.53,1:02:47.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chodil som aj na karate...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.70,1:02:49.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,externe!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.83,1:03:14.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Úžasné.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.20,1:03:17.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyhral?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.24,1:03:20.40,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Chcete zomrieť?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.72,1:03:25.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie je koniec. Nevidíte?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.55,1:03:37.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zaujímavé.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.18,1:03:40.51,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Veľmi zaujímavé.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.49,1:03:53.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že viem.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.13,1:04:07.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mám to. Tak ideme!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.67,1:04:32.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,On prehrá!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.99,1:04:34.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Poď chlapče!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.40,1:04:55.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.55,1:05:20.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zožer si to!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.81,1:05:40.14,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Platia naňho len intuitívne útoky.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.33,1:05:45.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.14,1:05:50.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je koniec? Je mŕtvy?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.52,1:05:52.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ešte nie.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.81,1:05:55.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie?!\NAko to myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.59,1:05:59.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Len prekvapivé útoky zaberajú. \NZneviditeľním sa.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.16,1:06:02.24,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale mal by si ho doraziť!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.07,1:06:04.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To je riskantné.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.11,1:06:11.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hergot...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.45,1:06:19.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je to riskantné.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.66,1:06:22.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Viem.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.81,1:06:24.39,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.31,1:06:27.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,niekto to urobiť musí.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.51,1:06:30.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.15,1:07:03.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.76,1:07:13.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Suzuki! Suziki prečo!?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.85,1:07:16.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tvoj brat...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.87,1:07:20.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,čaká na teba.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.26,1:07:25.95,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Suzuki! Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.70,1:07:55.13,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Reika.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.37,1:07:58.22,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Postaraj sa o Suzukiho.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.39,1:08:00.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.08,1:08:02.26,MCSG,,0,0,0,,už je neskoro.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.17,1:08:06.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžeme ho zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.65,1:08:13.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,A čo ty?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.57,1:08:15.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dokončím to.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.28,1:08:19.18,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ukončím hru.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.48,1:08:22.80,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!\NNie!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.96,1:08:32.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde je ten druhý?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.41,1:08:34.67,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Bola s ním zábava.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.14,1:09:08.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zostaň tu. Zabijem ťa neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.87,1:09:15.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Hej! Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.51,1:09:23.02,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo teraz?\NMôžeme utiecť a nechať to na Okovi!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.14,1:09:24.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,A ak prehrá?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.84,1:09:26.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.44,1:09:29.84,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musíme dôjsť na to, ako vyhrať!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.00,1:09:31.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale to nejde!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.41,1:09:36.58,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme umrieť!\NObaja máme niekoho, kto nás potrebuje!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.78,1:09:43.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Preto to spravim.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.79,1:09:46.33,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Preto musím!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.84,1:09:50.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musím! Kto iný?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.24,1:09:54.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.84,1:09:57.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musíme!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.10,1:09:59.10,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Reika.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:03.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale ako môžeme poraziť to monštrum?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.68,1:10:07.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Oka povedal, že ho musíme prekvapiť.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.32,1:10:09.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,No ako ho prekvapíme?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.37,1:10:12.28,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mohli by sme ho odstreliť.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.04,1:10:17.68,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.29,1:10:23.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budem návnada. Keď sa \Npriblíži, odstrelíte ho zdiaľky.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.06,1:10:26.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čože?! Zošalel si?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.84,1:10:32.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nemáme na výber.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.44,1:10:39.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkaj! Si si tým plánom istý?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.90,1:11:14.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ayumu.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.84,1:11:22.63,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.73,1:11:26.47,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počúvaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.21,1:11:30.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Musím to povedať predtým, než pôjdem.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.82,1:11:33.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.11,1:11:38.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Znamenáš pre mňa veľa.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.56,1:11:45.06,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prosím nezomri!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.16,1:11:49.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nezomri, okej?!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.73,1:11:53.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,To nemám v úmysle.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.12,1:11:58.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Myslíš to vážne?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.33,1:12:01.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Fakt to myslíš vážne?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.32,1:12:03.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.46,1:12:09.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nevzdám sa ani keby \Nokolnosti boli proti mne.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.01,1:12:17.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sľúb mi!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.99,1:12:21.53,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak prežiješ, budeme \Nvšetci štyria bývať spolu!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.32,1:12:26.17,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty, tvoj brat, ja a môj chlapec!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.16,1:12:31.07,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dobre? Sľúb.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.70,1:12:38.12,MCSG,,0,0,0,,No táák!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.20,1:12:43.37,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Proste povedz ,,áno" keď sa ťa na to pýtajú!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.78,1:12:49.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.40,1:12:53.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Je to sľub.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.18,1:12:57.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Neporuš ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.86,1:13:05.14,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ochránim ťa!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.51,1:13:08.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nenechám ťa zomrieť!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.31,1:13:13.01,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Sleduj ako ho prederavím!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.39,1:13:24.55,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dostanem sa domov.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.77,1:13:29.43,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Určite.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.99,1:13:38.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo to...?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.53,1:14:16.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ešte nie sú na miestach....
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.40,1:14:30.73,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Počkaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.72,1:14:35.75,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dovoľ mi spýtať sa.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.60,1:14:38.97,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Prečo...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.02,1:14:42.56,MCSG,,0,0,0,,sa zabíjame?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.31,1:14:48.83,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Cítiš, že si v prítomnosti Boha?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.35,1:14:50.57,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Boh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.38,1:14:55.96,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Boh je absolútna moc.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.21,1:14:59.99,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ty si Boh...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.88,1:15:02.81,MCSG,,0,0,0,,však?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.06,1:15:08.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tento svet má veľa Bohov. \NJa som len jedným z nich.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.00,1:15:13.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nedá sa to poprieť.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.00,1:15:21.52,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zásah!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.97,1:15:32.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zabijem ťa!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.66,1:15:35.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Skap.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.32,1:15:37.90,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Skap!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.70,1:15:47.14,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Iste.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.88,1:15:48.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.79,1:15:54.27,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžem ho doraziť!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.28,1:16:03.63,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vôbec nemieri.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.87,1:16:27.42,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nieeee!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.17,1:16:59.45,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.43,1:18:46.25,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dostal som posledného bossa.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.02,1:20:49.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Koniec.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.05,1:20:53.59,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu, je koniec.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.80,1:22:28.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale mne...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.89,1:22:32.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,mne už nešlo pomôcť!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.85,1:22:34.70,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ani mne.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.10,1:22:37.16,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Všetko spravil Kato.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.04,1:22:40.71,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.51,1:22:42.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.07,1:22:46.21,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.53,1:22:49.10,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.74,1:22:51.61,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Spravil toho toľko...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.81,1:22:53.22,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Gantz.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.91,1:22:56.15,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ukáž mi skóre.
