Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.51,1:24:37.05,MCSG1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baldy, 2 body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.51,1:24:37.05,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Celkovo 4{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.93,1:24:42.38,MCSG1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nishi, 12 bodov.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.93,1:24:42.38,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Celkovo 35{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.76,1:24:48.25,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Si na rade Kato.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.89,1:24:56.34,MCSG1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kato-cha, LOL, 100 bodov.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.90,1:24:56.34,MCSG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Celkovo 100{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.68,1:24:58.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Úžasné!\NSakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.71,1:25:00.44,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zvládol si to!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.04,1:25:02.76,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zvládol...?
