Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.70,1:25:27.74,MCSG,,0,0,0,,2. VZKRIESIŤ MŔTVEHO HRÁČA.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.78,1:25:29.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,3. VYMAZANIE SPOMIENOK A KONIEC.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.96,1:25:32.10,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyber si trojku a budeš voľný.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.35,1:25:36.32,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa k pokojnému životu s bratom.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.68,1:25:38.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Teším sa s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.75,1:25:40.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kato.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.84,1:25:43.35,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.46,1:25:45.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Zbohom.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.47,1:25:47.04,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ži dobrý život.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.22,1:26:28.91,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nie som mŕtva...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.20,1:26:42.29,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ten idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.18,1:26:46.94,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ten pokrytec!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.30,1:26:56.78,MCSG,,0,0,0,,KATO-CHA (LOL), 100 BODOV
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.19,1:27:15.31,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Myslíš, že bola vzkriesená?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.32,1:27:18.79,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ale prečo Kato?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.98,1:27:21.72,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Čo tvoj brat?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.34,1:27:25.20,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Budeš sa musieť znova zapojiť do hry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.46,1:27:27.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Mohol by si zomrieť.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.20,1:27:31.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Dal som jej sľub.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.00,1:27:40.25,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Slabošské.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.52,1:27:47.00,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Môžem odísť?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.15,1:27:56.11,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Doma ma čaká brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.99,1:28:16.66,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Katovi si nepovedal, \Nže s nami zvykol bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.83,1:28:18.60,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Tvoj brat čaká.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.56,1:28:22.54,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ber trojku.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.27,1:28:26.98,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.25,1:28:39.09,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Ak by mohol, bojoval by za vzkriesenie \Nvšetkých, čo kedy v hre zomreli.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.26,1:28:41.02,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.94,1:28:51.41,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vyberám si tretí. Vysloboď ma.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.92,1:29:01.62,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Nikdy som si nemyslel, že sa vráti!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.57,1:29:06.14,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Vôbec sa nezmenil.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.45,1:29:11.87,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Preňho je to vždy o tom istom.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.27,1:29:16.09,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Riskuje svoj život pre dobro iných.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.97,1:29:21.19,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Aj Kurono taký bol.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.42,1:29:27.85,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Spravím to isté.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.29,1:29:31.89,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Jedného dňa...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.51,1:29:35.86,MCSG,,0,0,0,,oživím Kurona.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.05,1:29:51.93,MCSG,,0,0,0,,Som doma!
